---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'

import { Button, Icon } from 'astro-pure/user'
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/CommonPage.astro'

const headings = [
  { depth: 2, slug: 'github-activity', text: 'GitHub Activity' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'projects', text: 'Projects' }
]
---

<PageLayout title='Projects' {headings}>
  <div class='not-prose flex justify-center'>
    <a
      href='https://github.com/Atingaii'
      target='_blank'
      class='flex items-center gap-x-3 rounded-full border bg-background px-4 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md'
    >
      <span class='size-2 rounded-full bg-green-400'></span>
      <p class='font-medium text-muted-foreground'>Visit GitHub Profile</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <h2 id='github-activity'>GitHub Activity</h2>
  <p>
    <Image
      src='https://ghchart.rshah.org/659eb9/Atingaii'
      alt='Atingaii GitHub contribution activity chart'
      inferSize
      loading='lazy'
    />
  </p>
  <p>
    这里记录的是我在 GitHub 上的公开活跃度。对我来说，它不仅是提交记录，也是一段持续学习、做项目和整理思路的过程痕迹。
  </p>

  <h2 id='projects'>Projects</h2>
  <div class='not-prose rounded-3xl border border-border/70 bg-gradient-to-b from-card to-muted/40 p-5 shadow-sm'>
    <div class='mb-4 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3'>
      <div class='space-y-1'>
        <p class='text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-foreground'>Current Project</p>
        <h3 class='text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground'>LumenCV</h3>
      </div>
      <span class='rounded-full border border-border bg-background/80 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground'>
        GitHub
      </span>
    </div>
    <p class='mb-5 leading-7 text-muted-foreground'>
      这是一个偏实用型的简历模板项目，核心目标是用尽量简单的方式维护中文技术简历：
      直接修改单个 HTML 文件，在浏览器里预览，并导出为一页 A4 PDF。它不追求复杂交互，
      更强调简洁、正式和可维护，适合拿来快速整理实习或校招方向的个人简历。
      仓库地址是
      <a href='https://github.com/Atingaii/LumenCV' target='_blank'>Atingaii/LumenCV</a>。
    </p>
    <div class='flex flex-wrap gap-3'>
      <Button href='https://github.com/Atingaii/LumenCV' target='_blank' title='查看仓库'>
        <Icon class='size-5' name='github' slot='before' />
      </Button>
      <Button href='https://github.com/Atingaii' target='_blank' title='查看 GitHub'>
        <Icon class='size-5' name='link' slot='before' />
      </Button>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>

